# Sonix — Mobile App Environment Configuration

# Backend API URL (Laravel server)
# Example: https://sonix-api.yourdomain.com/api
# For local development: http://192.168.x.x:8000/api
EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://your-api-domain.com/api

# === Optional: Expo Push Notifications ===
# Get from https://expo.dev/accounts/[username]/settings/access-tokens
# EXPO_PUBLIC_PUSH_TOKEN=your_push_token
